  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ゼロワンSPは、2004年に日本のみでリリースされたテキストアドベンチャーゲームです。プレイヤーは、調査と対話を組み合わせたフェーズの中で、自身を取り巻く謎の鍵を発見しなければなりません。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Nagoya always suffers from mysterious dreams. One day he is invited by his classmates on a drinking party to celebrate the last day of semester. They hear piano playing at night school. Depending on actions, the mystery can have four absolutely different and often fantastic reasons.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
